    dc:title "A review of Palaearctic Metachrostis Hübner, [1820] 1816 with description of three new species (Lepidoptera: Noctuidae, Eublemminae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274740>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274743>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274746> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274740>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Metachrostis spp., adults. 1. M. dardouini, male, Europe (ZFMK); 2. M. dardouini, male, France (ZISP); 3. M. velox, female, France (ZISP); 4. M. velocior, male, Europe (ZFMK); 5. M. velocior, male, Greece, Creta (ZFMK); 6. M. velocior, male, Turkey, Adana (ZISP); 7. M. velocior, male, Algeria (ZISP); 8. M. griseimargo, male, Algeria (ZISP)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/274740/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274743>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23 – 28. Metachrostis spp., genitalia and tergite 8 of male. 23. M. dardouini, prep. 0 0 47 Matov, Austria, Vindabona, (ZISP); 24. M. velox, prep. 0 0 49 Matov, Italy, Sardinia (ZISP); 25. M. velocior, prep. 0 0 28 Matov, Lebanon, Beirut (ZISP); 26. M. griseimargo, prep. 0 0 50 Matov, Algeria (ZISP); 27. M. djakonovi, holotype, prep. 0 0 27 Matov, East Kazakhstan, Djarkent (ZISP); 28. M. djakonovi, paratype, prep. 0 0 65 Matov, West Kazakhstan, Mangistau (ZISP)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/274743/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274746>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37 – 45. Eublemminae spp., female genitalia. 37. Metachrostis dardouini, prep. 0 0 59 Matov, Hungary, Gant (ZISP); 38. M. velox, prep. 0 0 64 Matov, France (ZISP); 39. M. velocior, prep. 0 0 43 Matov, Malta (ZISP); 40. M. quinaria, prep. 0 0 42 Matov, North India (ZISP); 41. M. sinevi, paratype, prep. Dubatolov, in glycerine, Russia, Khabarovsk terr.; 42. Odice arcuinna, prep. 0 0 63 Matov, Hungary (ZISP); 43. Eublemma amoena, prep. 4767 GB, Spain (ZFMK); 44. Eublemma melabela, prep. 0 0 52 Matov (ZISP); 45. Rhypagia lacernaria, prep. 0 0 61 Matov, Spain (ZISP)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/274746/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

